  "body": "There used to be a choice for `advanced typescript project` (it might be different if I remember it wrong) when starting a project wit `npx hardhat`.\r\n\r\nBut there is no choice for the advanced anymore and in [the doc](https://hardhat.org/hardhat-runner/docs/guides/project-setup), nothing is mentioned about it.\r\n\r\nIt was helpful for me so I liked it and used it.\r\n\r\nHas it been removed for some reasons?",
